    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, and i definitely want to include the critique in my paper. but for the sake of the actual evolutionary timeline, wouldn't it still be accurate to say that some cultures are just naturally more advanced in their social development than others? like, is there a distinction to be made between cultures that have progressed toward a modern state and those that have stayed in a more traditional, tribal state?",
